{"tid":2269974,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"螞蟻今伏｜H股被「麵神」祝福後即煞停 麵咪媽：「⋯⋯」","createTime":"2020-11-03T20:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T23:37:48.000Z","uid":7076,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e74ebc9b611adbc6dede77e39a96dbfc7689e45a","tid":2269974,"uid":7076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T20:21:34.000Z","msg":"螞蟻A股煞停，日前表示「all in 炒螞蟻」的麵咪媽最新接受本報訪問時表示：「我都唔知點算😑」<br />\n<br />\n他原本計劃周三沽清日清，為螞蟻上市準備資金，更指「80蚊升80% easy money」問到明日部署，「嘩 ，睇氣氛啦。佢無啦啦咁爆左單新聞出嚟，好難搞架喎，睇聽日呀里爸爸（阿里巴巴）咩環境先再採取行動😡」他透露未有抽螞蟻，「抽個日趕唔切抽😂」<br />\n<br />\n至於螞蟻H股去向，麵咪媽作最後祝福：「上到嘅🤔」惟正當此報道準備出街之時，接獲港交所（388）回應，指其獲螞蟻集團通知，其決定暫緩在上海及香港的上市。麵麵收到有關消息後表示：「.....」問到心情如何：「輕鬆」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201103/R5LATOVQYVDKZEDA3EEUURCB44/?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201103%2FR5LATOVQYVDKZEDA3EEUURCB44%2F%3F&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=d8f66413\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201103%2FR5LATOVQYVDKZEDA3EEUURCB44%2F%3F&h=bda1d0f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201103/R5LATOVQYVDKZEDA3EEUURCB44/?</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ae13d7f2cb610749cc1c09e6bab467fa182d53","tid":2269974,"uid":289259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T21:37:35.000Z","msg":"神蹟降臨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd17a3be58361124c9916faf7d2048259aa72fad","tid":2269974,"uid":13914,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T21:38:59.000Z","msg":"d emoji 真係畫龍點睛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de50fc18e28d0f0463df56110e0cbc4dfb0e7560","tid":2269974,"uid":132898,"like":8,"dislike":0,